    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "This blog covers the second half of my spring break trip, in which I traveled to Bali and Jakarta.  The trip began the morning after I got back from Malaysia.  Due to this fact (and because my alarm was set to the quietest possible volume), I may have not woken up in time for my flight and had to leave later in the day.  The photos start from the day after I flew in."
    },
