        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "We stayed in Kuta, which is in the south of the island.  To begin the day, we took a taxi from our residence to Ubud, which was a bit over an hour drive north.  We walked the streets and saw a few sights, and then took a hike up a hill nearby."
