    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "The plan after that was to head to a gate and then to a large temple, but we ran out of daylight before heading to the temple.  There was also a holiday during our stay, so the roads in some areas we went to were packed.  We stayed at the gate for a short bit and then took a long drive back."
    },
